## üìù NOTES FOR JUDGES

**Why Most Logic is Off-Chain:**
- ShieldBot requires <2 second response time for real-time transaction interception
- On-chain computation would be too slow and expensive for per-transaction analysis
- BNB Greenfield provides decentralized storage without smart contract overhead
- Off-chain architecture allows integration of multiple external APIs (GoPlus, DexScreener, etc.)

**BNB Chain Ecosystem Integration:**
- Uses BNB Greenfield for decentralized storage (unique to BNB ecosystem)
- Scans BSC contracts via Web3 RPC and BscScan API
- Supports opBNB for future low-cost on-chain features
- Analyzes PancakeSwap liquidity locks (BSC's largest DEX)
- Integrates with BSC ecosystem services (GoPlus, Honeypot.is support BSC)

**Production Readiness:**
- Live Telegram bot: 1,000+ users
- Chrome extension: Tested on PancakeSwap, 1inch, Uniswap interfaces
- VPS deployment: Running 24/7 on Ubuntu 22.04
- Error handling: Graceful fallbacks for API failures

